data.title: 2009 - 10 Season - Arsenal Results & Scores PDF
data.meta_description: 2009_10 Season - Arsenal Results & Scores.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document lists all of Arsenal's matches from their 2009/2010 season across competitions like the Premier League, Champions League, and domestic cups. It shows the date of each match, the opposing team, and the final scoreline. Arsenal played a total of around 50 matches that season across various competitions in England and Europe.
